Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Adonisklage Mythologie Adonis"

- Photo of an engraving of the 'Lamentation of Christ'
- Extracts from different publications
- Notes about 'Venus Mourning the Death of Adonis'
- Correspondence with Tieschowitz (dated 1943) and with Schidlauski (dated 1941)
